---
layout: page
title: home
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
---
<article class="center__full switcher">
  <div class="col-l flow">
    <section class="flow">
      <h2>Introduction.</h2>
      <p>My name is William. Among other <a
          href="https://williamwhitaker.art">things</a>, I'm
        a front-end developer.</p>
      <div class="center">
        <h3>Some competencies:</h3>
        <ul role="list">
          <li>HTML</li>
          <li>CSS</li>
          <li>JavaScript</li>
          <li>PHP</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="flow">
      <h2>Thoughtables.</h2>
      <div id="posts">
        {% set postslist = collections.posts %}
        {% include 'partials/postslist.njk' %}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <div class="col-r">
    <section class="flow intrinsic-center">
      <aside class="wide-box">
        <h2>A call to action!</h2>
        <p>Got a project you'd like help with?</p>
        <p>Let's <a href="mailto:{{ env.EMAIL_ADDRESS }}">talk</a>!
        </p>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </div>
</article>
